prompts.frontCover:
A comic book style birthday card front cover featuring two people, Lao Lao and Jordan, from reference image e8028c5e-f934-41b7-9b60-b2f256376440. In the center, a 2D cartoon illustration of Lao Lao, a young East Asian woman in her early 20s with long dark straight hair, thin-rimmed glasses, and a happy smiling expression, is depicted as a queen. She sits on an ornate golden throne, wearing a majestic royal gown and a crown. She playfully bonks Jordan on the head with a scepter. Jordan, a young Southeast Asian man in his early 20s with short black hair and a big joyful smile, is kneeling beside the throne, wearing a colorful jester's outfit with a jester hat. The scene is dynamic and energetic, with bold outlines, vibrant colors, and subtle halftone patterns. A large banner hangs above the throne with the text "Another Year of Ruling". In the safe center area, the words "Happy Birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The background has action lines and a "KAPOW!" sound effect bubble, enhancing the funny, lighthearted, and exciting superhero comic book feel. --ar 5:7 --style raw

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
